Effective: 5th July 2023
This Privacy Policy describes how Slack collects, uses and discloses information associated with an identified or identifiable individual (referred to in this Privacy Policy as
‚ÄòPersonal Data‚Äô
) and what choices you have around this activity. If you have any questions, please don‚Äôt hesitate to contact us.
When we refer to ‚Äò
Slack
‚Äô, we mean Slack Technologies, LLC or Slack Technologies Limited, as explained in more detail in the ‚ÄòIdentifying the data controller and processor‚Äô section below.
